                                          <p><span style="color: #000000;">The results from the Irritable Bowel Syndrom stem cell treatment can last for years or even indefinitely. This is because the stem cells are reprogramming your immune system to work the way it was designed to work. Once the immune cells are reprogrammed and any damage is repaired at the intestines then things will work the way they should. This will last because it is real regeneration and not just a pill to cover up symptoms. </span></p>
