                              <p><span style="color: #000000;">The only side effects that have been documented are the following:</span></p>
                              <ul>
                                <li><span style="color: #000000;">1 in 100 people will experience a slight fever and/or headache for a few hours after treatment or the next day. We have found that 500mg of Tylenol easily resolves this issue.</span></li>
