                            <div class="dbc-widget-container">
                              <h2 class="dbc-heading-title dbc-size-default" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #00ccff;">The Traumatic Brain Injury Stem Cell Treatment at Dream Body Clinic</span></h2>
                            </div>
