                <div class="dbc-widget-container">
                  <div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-16dba41 r-1adg3ll r-1kt6imw" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3" style="color: #000000;"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw">The TKN Mesoject Gun, is a needle-free mesotherapy device that uses innovative technology to deliver PRP &amp; MSCs into the deeper layers of the skin. Here's how it works:</span></span></div><ul dir="ltr"><li><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41" dir="ltr"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw">Technology</span></span></span></strong><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><strong>:</strong> The device employs Electroporation Pulse Modulation (EPM) technology or Pulse Booster technology, depending on the model or description. </span></span></span></div><ul><li><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41" dir="ltr"><span style="color: #000000;"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw">Electroporation</span></span></span><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">: This involves the use of electrical impulses to generate temporary hydrophilic channels in the lipid bilayers of cell membranes and intercellular spaces. This process significantly increases the electrical conductivity and permeability of the tissue, allowing PRP &amp; MSCs to penetrate the skin locally, non-invasively, and painlessly.</span></span></span></div></li><li><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41" dir="ltr"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw">Pulse Booster Technology</span></span></span></strong><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-1kt6imw"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><strong>:</strong> This combines electroporation with microabrasion. The device emits perfect square wave pulses at low frequency and low voltage, enabling the precise and safe delivery of mesotherapy assets. Additionally, microabrasion is facilitated by microprotrusions on the device heads, which help in the superficial scraping of the horny layer to enhance the entry and uniform distribution of the PRP &amp; MSCs.</span></span></span></div></li><li><span style="color: #000000;">This device stands out for its ability to offer effective transdermal delivery of PRP &amp; MSCs without the invasiveness of needles.</span></li></ul></li></ul>
                </div>
