      <section class="dbc-section dbc-top-section dbc-element dbc-element-e149404 dbc-section-boxed dbc-section-height-default dbc-section-height-default" data-id="e149404" data-element_type="section">
        <div class="dbc-container dbc-column-gap-default">
          <div class="dbc-column dbc-col-100 dbc-top-column dbc-element dbc-element-690d810" data-id="690d810" data-element_type="column">
            <div class="dbc-widget-wrap dbc-element-populated">
              <div class="dbc-element dbc-element-e0df49c dbc-widget dbc-widget-text-editor" data-id="e0df49c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
                <div class="dbc-widget-container">
                  <p><span style="color: #000000;">It is our opinion that the Stem Cell Facial Treatment is a superior alternative to botox, but don't fret if you have already done botox because the benefits of the stem cell facial still apply. The great part about botox is that it immediately reduces or eliminates wrinkles. The stem cell facial will do the same, but more gradually because it is creating real collagen repair and restoration.</span></p><ol><li><span style="color: #000000;">Botox weakens the facial muscles while the stem cells strengthen facial muscles. Over time this makes a huge difference</span></li><li><span style="color: #000000;">Botox requires frequent follow up treatments to maintain results. The Stem Cell Facial Treatment creates real cellular regeneration that will last for years.</span></li><li><span style="color: #000000;">Botox limits facial motion while the stem cell facial treatment has no negative effect on facial mobility</span></li></ol><p><span style="color: #000000;">Botox and Fillers do not prevent us from performing the stem cell facial. Botox is great at immediately eliminating hard wrinkle lines and can be done before stem cell treatment for instant effect. The stem cell facial can then be done after to ensure that those wrinkle lines don't come back.</span></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
